reviewText: THANK YOU, great service, DVD delivered in good quality! :)

I highly recommend this vendor for the speedy delivery of the dvd. I appreciate it's timeliness to deliver. This movie is a feel good movie about two teen best friends...and one falls for the other. What follows is a story of  love, heartbreak, and ultimately, self-acceptance. It's a typical story, but the two leads have great chemistry and it puts a smile on your face!
